（民77）。我國消費者教育情意教學目標的探討。國立臺灣師範大學家政教育研究所碩士論文，未出版，臺北市。蕭新煌（民74）。對國內外消費者運動的一些觀察（下）。中國論壇，14（2），41-45。龔群（民90）。道德烏托邦的重構——哈伯瑪斯交往倫理思想研究。臺北市：洪葉文化。西文部分Baudrillard, J. (1983). Simulations. New York. : Semiotext.Bannister, R & Monsma, C (1982). Classification of concepts in consumer education. West Chicago, IL：South-Western.Bocock , R. (1993). Consumption. London ; New York : Routledge.Canabal , M. E. (2002). Decision making styles of young south Indian consumers : an exploratory study. College Student Journal, 36(1), 12-19.Corrigan, P. (1997). The sociology of consumption: An introduction. London: Sage.Davis, K. (1995). Reshaping the Female Body: the Dilemma of Cosmetic Surgery. New York: Routledge.Garman, E. (1991). Consumer economic issues in America . Boston : Houghton Mifflin.Guest, J. (2002). Consumers and consumerism in America today . The Journal of consumer Affairs, 36(2), 139-149.Havighurst , R. & Chickering , A. (1981).The life cycle. In A. Chickering (Ed.), The modern American college ( pp. 16-50) . San Francisco : Jossey-Bass.Herrmann, A. (2002). Shopping for identities : Gender and consumer culture. Feminist Studies. 28 (3), 539-549.Kellner, D. (1992). Popular culture and the construction of post-modern identities, in S. Lash and J. Friedman (eds) , Modernity and identity (pp. 141-177). Oxford, UK : Blackwell.Lunt, P. K., & Livingstone, S. M. (1992). Mass consumer and personal identity. Buckingham : Open University.Lury, C. (1996). Consumer culture. Cambridge : Polity.Murphy, P.D., Cavanaugh, H.P., Geer, C., Plihal, J., Elsbemd, L. & Norman, M. (1974). Consumer education curriculum models: A spiral-process approach. North Dakota State University. (ED095271)Opare-Obisaw, C., Brakohiapa, L., Lokko, P. & Kudjawu, B. D. (2003).The influence of advertisement on the choice and use of processed food, beverages and drinks by teenagers. Journal of ARAHE, Vol.10, 27 - 34.Rosner, B. (1995). Fundamentals of Biostatistics (4th ed.). Boston, MA.: Wadsworth.Ross-Gordon, J. M. (199